         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Success! Hommage to the Bhagavant! In the 11th year of King Vāsiṭṭhīputta Siri-Sātakaṇṇi, on the 1st fortnight of the rainy season, on the 1th day. The pious gift of Saṅghaka, the brother of the renunciant Kaṇhasiri.</p>
         </div>
